These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, water
3 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, scrabble
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, videographer, lawyer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, sunflower
1. the person playing canasta is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the software-developer is the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking water is the person playing scrabble##1
7. the lawyer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Beverage      | water  | juice       | mirinda   |
| Game          | scrabble | monopoly | canasta |
| Job         | software-developer  | lawyer | videographer    |
| Flower   | sunflower | azalea       | dahlia      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, martial-arts
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, traveling
House: cottage, ranch-style, futuristic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, funk, soul
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
6. the fan of soul is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific      | superhero  | martial-arts        |
| Hobby         | traveling | singing | rock-climbing |
| House   | cottage | ranch-style | futuristic       |
| Music-Genre           | soul     | funk     | blues      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, january
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose, poppy
3 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the person who growspoppy is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Birthday      | february    | august        | january |
| Flower           | rose    | poppy | orchid    |
| Pet   | mouse | rat             | pony  |
| Transport     | train     | bus                | subway  |

