.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, marigold, bellflower
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, art-deco
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, western
3 different pets are kept: rat, goat, horse
1. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who growsrose is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Flower          | marigold    | bellflower  | rose      |
| House           | art-deco    | gothic-revival | cape-cod |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | horror  | drama     |
| Pet   | rat | goat    | horse      |

