.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, singing, video-games
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, baccarat, cain
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower, bellflower
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, spanish, pakistani
1. the person who growsdahlia is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the spanish is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the thai is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is the bolivar-smoker##1
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking     | singing   |
| Cigar           | cain       | baccarat   | bolivar     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | dahlia | bellflower |
| Nationality           | pakistani      | thai         | spanish  |

