.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cherry, spinach
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, siglo, montecristo
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, 7up
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, accountant, chef
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person eating cherry is on the left of the chef##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Food          | asparagus | cherry       | spinach |
| Cigar   | montecristo     | pall-mall       | siglo   |
| Beverage           | juice      | lemonade       | 7up     |
| Job         | social-worker   | accountant | chef  |

