The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, police-officer
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, domino
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, handball, rowing
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| City          | prague       | new-york         | nizza   |
| Job           | accountant | police-officer | dressmaker |
| Game   | mah-jongg     | scrabble        | domino        |
| Sport   | handball      | cricket           | rowing        |

