The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, handball, basketball
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, chestnut, aquamarine
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, malaysian, dutch
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is the dutch##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the mexican is the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | woodworking | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | parkour | basketball         | handball       |
| Color           | apricot      | aquamarine      | chestnut         |
| Nationality     | malaysian      | dutch         | mexican          |

