There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, colombian
1. the colombian is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person eating pepper is the dutch##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Food       | pepper            | asparagus      | lemon  |
| Flower         | daffodil | amaryllis | aconite |
| Pet         | goat               | guinea-pig | goldfish |
| Nationality   | dutch             | colombian       | brazilian      |

