3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the russian##1
6. the french is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Flower           | rose | dahlia         | begonia |
| Beverage   | mirinda      | juice | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality   | british   | french       | russian     |
