There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, blood-red, green
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, french, thai
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, puzzles, gardening
1. the thai is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Pet           | lizard | frog | turtle |
| Color   | green        | blood-red       | pink     |
| Nationality   | french     | thai         | dutch     |
| Hobby     | gardening | puzzles          | photography      |

