The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, manager, scientist
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, epic, spy
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the trike is the person who likes white##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person who likes green is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person who likes turquise is the manager##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the scientist is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Color         | green | white | turquise   |
