3 different games are played: poker, go, scrabble
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, aquamarine, purple
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, ambient, d&b
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the person drinking water is the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage    | coffee | sprite     | water      |
| Game        | poker | go       | scrabble |
| Color       | aquamarine | blood-red | purple  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | indie   | d&b  |

