3. the fan of dubstep is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking coffee is in the middle##1
6. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |
