2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
6. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | milk    | cola    |
| City          | boston         | liverpool    | san-francisco   |
| Birthday           | november | march | december |
| Color   | blue         | grey     | purple    |

