The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, cherrycher
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, canasta
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person watching cherrycher movies is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person eating cherry is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person playing bridge is the person eating watermelon##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Food      | watermelon         | cherry     | cabbage     |
| Movie-Genre           | superhero        | cherrycher | scientific |
| Game   | bridge        | canasta   | mah-jongg    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rugby   | water-polo |

