.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, art-deco
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, traveling
City: hamburg, liverpool, hannover
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, musician, analyst
1. the art-deco house is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the musician##1
4. the photographer is on the far left##1
5. the musician is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| House          | art-deco     | gothic-revival    | craftsman    |
| Hobby         | collecting | traveling | hiking     |
| City   | hamburg  | liverpool      | hannover        |
| Job         | photographer   | musician   | analyst |

 